'''拉梅洛·鲍尔'''（{{lang-en|'''LaMelo Ball'''}}，{{bd|2001年|8月22日|catIdx=B}}）是[[美国|美国]]男子[[篮球|篮球]]运动员，现效力於[[NBA|NBA]][[夏洛特黃蜂|夏洛特黃蜂]]，主打[[控球后卫|控球后卫]]。是[[朗素·波爾|朗素·波爾]]与[[李安傑洛·鮑爾|李安傑洛·鮑爾]]的弟弟。

== 早期生涯 ==
拉梅洛的父母[[拉瓦尔·鲍尔|拉瓦尔·鲍尔]]和蒂娜·鲍尔都曾是大学篮球运动员。拉瓦尔·鲍尔身高1.98米，先后效力于[[华盛顿州|华盛顿州]]和加州州立大学洛杉矶分校。蒂娜身高1.8米，效力于[[加州大学洛杉矶分校|加州大学洛杉矶分校]]。其兄長為[[芝加哥公牛|芝加哥公牛]]的主控[[朗佐·鮑爾|朗佐·鮑爾]]，在他的童年拉梅洛打球的对手都要比他大几岁。他13岁的时候，身高1.7米。在一场和16岁、17岁球员的比赛中，他拿下29分。

== 高中生涯 ==
[[File:20160330_MCDAAG_Lonzo_Ball_at_the_top_of_the_key_(cropped).jpg|右]]
拉梅洛身高2.01米，是一個相對高的控球後衛，臂展大。早在他的高中生涯時，他原本主要考慮當射手，然而目前他被認為是一個精通三分線外投球，同時在線内也有極佳的能力。拉梅洛經常嘗試三分球，這讓人們把它和柯瑞相比較。
2015年6月，拉梅洛进入加州奇诺岗市奇诺岗高中打球，跟随球队主教练史蒂夫·拜克学习。他的兄弟朗佐和利安杰洛，以及表弟安德烈·鲍尔都在这支名为“哈士奇队”的球队打球。<ref name="latimes2">{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/la-sp-ball-brothers-sondheimer-20150427-column.html|title=It's Ball in the family at Chino Hills basketball|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=April 26, 2015|last1=Sondheimer|first1=Eric|website=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211080956/http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/la-sp-ball-brothers-sondheimer-20150427-column.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
在6月16日对阵约翰·缪尔高中的比赛中，拉梅洛首次亮相就拿下27分和5个三分球。<ref name="debut">{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/varsity-times/la-sp-vi-boys-basketball-freshman-lamelo-ball-makes-quite-a-debut-for-chino-hills-20150616-story.html|title=Boys' basketball: LaMelo Ball, 13, makes quite a debut for Chino Hill|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=June 16, 2015|website=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211081342/http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/varsity-times/la-sp-vi-boys-basketball-freshman-lamelo-ball-makes-quite-a-debut-for-chino-hills-20150616-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在6月27日和Centennial高中的比赛中拿到20分。<ref name="corona">{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/varsity-times/la-sp-vi-boys-basketball-chino-hills-runs-past-corona-centennial-102-76-20150626-story.html|title=Boys' basketball: Chino Hills runs past Corona Centennial, 102-76|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=June 27, 2015|last1=Sondheimer|first1=Eric|website=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211080312/http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/varsity-times/la-sp-vi-boys-basketball-chino-hills-runs-past-corona-centennial-102-76-20150626-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在夏末新赛季，拉梅洛口头承诺大学将入读加州大学洛杉矶分校打球。<ref name="trifecta">{{cite web|url=http://www.scout.com/college/basketball/recruiting/story/1569074-lamelo-ball-completes-trifecta-for-bruins|title=LaMelo Ball completes trifecta for Bruins|accessdate=July 31, 2015|date=July 31, 2015|last1=Harrington|first1=Rob|website=[[Scout.com|Scout.com]]|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211081804/http://www.scout.com/college/basketball/recruiting/story/1569074-lamelo-ball-completes-trifecta-for-bruins|dead-url=no}}</ref>他成为了三个兄弟中第三个这么做的。<ref name="uclacommit">{{cite web|url=http://www.cbssports.com/college-basketball/news/ucla-accepts-verbal-commitment-from-13-year-old-star-lamelo-ball/|title=UCLA accepts verbal commitment from 13-year-old star LaMelo Ball|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=August 1, 2015|last1=Parrish|first1=Gary|website=''[[CBS_Sports|CBS Sports]]''|archive-date=2017-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170213173215/http://www.cbssports.com/college-basketball/news/ucla-accepts-verbal-commitment-from-13-year-old-star-lamelo-ball/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在11月30日以131-42的比分战胜球圣贝纳迪诺高中的比赛中，鲍尔拿下20分。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/varsity-times/la-sp-vi-boys-basketball-chino-hills-opens-with-131-42-victory-20151130-story.html|title=Chino Hills opens with 131-42 victory|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=November 30, 2015|last1=Sondheimer|first1=Eric|website=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211081120/http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/varsity-times/la-sp-vi-boys-basketball-chino-hills-opens-with-131-42-victory-20151130-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年3月，奇诺冈打败塞拉峡谷高中，赢得了加州校际的联合会(CIF)南部部分开放部门锦标赛，拉梅洛17投11中，贡献26分。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/la-sp-chino-hills-sierra-canyon-20160306-column.html|title=Chino Hills defeats Sierra Canyon, 105-83, for first section title|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=March 5, 2016|last1=Sondheimer|first1=Eric|website=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211075957/http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/la-sp-chino-hills-sierra-canyon-20160306-column.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>这个月晚些时候,哈士奇队成为全国排名最高的州冠军球队。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maxpreps.com/news/ExPKqpH_ZUSLpZujM1f2Lg/no-1-chino-hills-runs-away-from-bishop-montgomery,-punches-ticket-to-california-state-championship-game.htm|title=No. 1 Chino Hills runs away from Bishop Montgomery, punches ticket to California state championship game|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=March 21, 2016|website=MaxPreps.com|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211075303/http://www.maxpreps.com/news/ExPKqpH_ZUSLpZujM1f2Lg/no-1-chino-hills-runs-away-from-bishop-montgomery,-punches-ticket-to-california-state-championship-game.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月27日，拉梅洛得到14分和5次助攻，帮助奇诺冈高中战胜赛尔高中。哈士奇队以35-0的完美记录结束了这一赛季。<ref name="flurry">{{cite web|url=http://www.maxpreps.com/news/j_MSlbiD1UeuK8wsiJPZOA/top-ranked-chino-hills-finishes-perfect-season-with-a-flurry.htm|title=Top-ranked Chino Hills finishes perfect season with a flurry|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=March 27, 2017|last1=Stephens|first1=Mitch|website=MaxPreps.com|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211075955/http://www.maxpreps.com/news/j_MSlbiD1UeuK8wsiJPZOA/top-ranked-chino-hills-finishes-perfect-season-with-a-flurry.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>MaxPreps.com将拉梅洛和他的队友Onyeka Okongwu一同评为“年度最佳新人”。拉梅洛以场均16.4分和16.4次助攻的战绩，帮助球队赢得MaxPreps网全美男子篮球最佳新人阵容第一队。<ref name="espn">{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/mens-college-basketball/story/_/id/18268717/ucla-bruins-lonzo-ball-family-just-beginning-relationship|title=Lonzo is just the beginning of the Ball-UCLA pipeline|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=December 14, 2016|last1=Borzello|first1=Jeff|website=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|archive-date=2017-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170212082243/http://www.espn.com/mens-college-basketball/story/_/id/18268717/ucla-bruins-lonzo-ball-family-just-beginning-relationship|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maxpreps.com/news/VBO3zMrQQUSqQAWAQvODAA/2015-16-maxpreps-boys-basketball-freshman-all-american-team.htm|title=2015-16 MaxPreps Boys Basketball Freshman All-American Team|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=April 21, 2016|last1=Hickman|first1=Jason|website=MaxPreps.com|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211155523/http://www.maxpreps.com/news/VBO3zMrQQUSqQAWAQvODAA/2015-16-maxpreps-boys-basketball-freshman-all-american-team.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

拉梅洛高二时，奇诺岗高中失去顶级球员朗佐和教练史蒂夫。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maxpreps.com/news/I2T1sSMBfUub7DciPrRMtw/high-school-top-25-team-preview--no-15-chino-hills.htm|title=High School Top 25 team preview: No. 15 Chino Hills|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=November 9, 2016|website=MaxPreps.com|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211155216/http://www.maxpreps.com/news/I2T1sSMBfUub7DciPrRMtw/high-school-top-25-team-preview--no-15-chino-hills.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年11月30日，在对阵牧场基督教高中的比赛中，拉梅洛拿到 31分，而他的哥哥利安杰洛砍下72分。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/varsity-times/la-sp-vi-boys-basketball-liangelo-ball-scores-72-points-in-latest-chino-hills-scoring-outburst-20161130-story.html|title=Boys' basketball: LiAngelo Ball scores 72 points in latest Chino Hills scoring outburst|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=November 30, 2016|last1=Sondheimer|first1=Eric|website=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211075849/http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/varsity-times/la-sp-vi-boys-basketball-liangelo-ball-scores-72-points-in-latest-chino-hills-scoring-outburst-20161130-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>到了12月，拉梅洛场均为哈士奇队贡献超过30分。<ref name="slam">{{cite web|url=http://www.slamonline.com/college-hs/youngest-ball-brothers-15-year-old-lamelo-averaging-30-ppg/#zEmA2jjOXAS0PCzR.97|title=Youngest of the Ball Brothers, 15-Year-Old LaMelo, Is Averaging 30 PPG|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=December 6, 2016|website=[[Slam_(magazine)|Slam]]|archive-date=2017-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170228164345/http://www.slamonline.com/college-hs/youngest-ball-brothers-15-year-old-lamelo-averaging-30-ppg/#zEmA2jjOXAS0PCzR.97|dead-url=no}}</ref>12月下旬，拉梅洛几秒内在半场中进球。<ref name="drains">{{cite web|url=http://usatodayhss.com/2016/video-lamelo-ball-drains-half-court-shot-two-seconds-after-controlling-opening-tip|title=LaMelo Ball drains half-court shot two seconds after controlling opening tip|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=December 15, 2016|website=USA TODAY High School Sports|archive-date=2017-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301005837/http://usatodayhss.com/2016/video-lamelo-ball-drains-half-court-shot-two-seconds-after-controlling-opening-tip/|dead-url=no}}</ref>媒体都作了广泛报道，包括从ESPN、[[貝比·魯斯|CBS体育]]、体育画报。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.si.com/extra-mustard/2016/12/27/chino-hills-lamelo-lonzo-ball-calls-halfcourt-shot-video|title=Lonzo Ball’s little brother calling his halfcourt shot was as disrespectful as it gets|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=December 27, 2016|website=[[Sports_Illustrated|Sports Illustrated]]|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211074844/http://www.si.com/extra-mustard/2016/12/27/chino-hills-lamelo-lonzo-ball-calls-halfcourt-shot-video|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/mens-college-basketball/story/_/page/QTP_161227Ball/lamelo-ball-younger-brother-ucla-star-lonzo-ball-hit-deep-3-pointer-half-court|title=LaMelo Ball, younger brother of UCLA star Lonzo Ball, drills a 3-pointer from half court|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=December 27, 2016|website=''[[ESPN|ESPN]]''|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211080949/http://www.espn.com/mens-college-basketball/story/_/page/QTP_161227Ball/lamelo-ball-younger-brother-ucla-star-lonzo-ball-hit-deep-3-pointer-half-court|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbssports.com/college-basketball/news/watch-ucla-recruit-lamelo-ball-calls-halfcourt-shot-and-drills-it/|title=UCLA recruit LaMelo Ball calls halfcourt shot and drills it|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=December 27, 2016|last1=Boone|first1=Kyle|website=''[[CBS_Sports|CBS Sports]]''|archive-date=2017-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303142801/http://www.cbssports.com/college-basketball/news/watch-ucla-recruit-lamelo-ball-calls-halfcourt-shot-and-drills-it/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[斯蒂芬·库里|斯蒂芬·库里]]评论,说:“这是充足的自信。他做到了，我想知道他做过，而不是错过了。这很惊人，很难以置信。等他打电话给他的投篮[[贝比·鲁斯|贝比·鲁斯]]，像什么也没发生。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxsports.com/nba/story/stephen-curry-lamelo-ball-high-school-half-court-3-pointer-called-shot-babe-ruth-point-highlight-ruining-basketball-122916|title=Steph Curry praises high schooler's half-court 'Babe Ruth' 3-pointer|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=December 29, 2016|last1=Lynch|first1=Andrew|website=''[[Fox_Sports_(United_States)|Fox Sports]]''|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211075220/http://www.foxsports.com/nba/story/stephen-curry-lamelo-ball-high-school-half-court-3-pointer-called-shot-babe-ruth-point-highlight-ruining-basketball-122916|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年1月10日，拉梅洛得到了全队最高的35分，奇诺岗高中获得了52连胜。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maxpreps.com/news/6GaGnm1Da0SlyekiV6B7sg/chino-hills-puts-up-119-points-in-52nd-consecutive-win.htm|title=Chino Hills puts up 119 points in 52nd consecutive win|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=January 10, 2017|website=MaxPreps.com|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211080205/http://www.maxpreps.com/news/6GaGnm1Da0SlyekiV6B7sg/chino-hills-puts-up-119-points-in-52nd-consecutive-win.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>拉梅洛在2月5日第一次输了他的高中比赛，橡树山学院终结了哈士奇队的60连胜记录。<ref name="firstloss">{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/varsity-times/la-sp-chino-hills-oak-hill-20170205-story.html|title=Chino Hills takes first loss of the season in stride|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=February 5, 2017|last1=Sondheimer|first1=Eric|website=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|archive-date=2017-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301075539/http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/varsity-times/la-sp-chino-hills-oak-hill-20170205-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在他的下一次2月7日的比赛中，虽然利安杰洛因为脚踝受伤而缺席比赛，但他拿下92分，并以146 - 123的比分击败洛杉矶高中。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/varsity-times/la-sp-vi-boys-basketball-lamelo-ball-scores-92-points-in-chino-hills-victory-20170207-story.html|title=With his high-scoring brother out hurt, Chino Hills sophomore LaMelo Ball shoots for 92 points|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=February 7, 2017|last1=Sondheimer|first1=Eric|website=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|archive-date=2017-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301075508/http://www.latimes.com/sports/highschool/varsity-times/la-sp-vi-boys-basketball-lamelo-ball-scores-92-points-in-chino-hills-victory-20170207-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 仅在第二节，拉梅洛就获得63分。在整个比赛中，他61投37中。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/espn/story/_/id/18643348/ucla-bruins-commit-lamelo-ball-brother-lonzo-ball-scores-92-high-school-game|title=UCLA commit LaMelo Ball, brother of Lonzo, scores 92 in high school game|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=February 7, 2017|last1=Borzello|first1=Jeff|website=''[[ESPN|ESPN]]''|archive-date=2017-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170228234749/http://www.espn.com/espn/story/_/id/18643348/ucla-bruins-commit-lamelo-ball-brother-lonzo-ball-scores-92-high-school-game|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="92pointscbssports">{{cite web|url=http://www.cbssports.com/college-basketball/news/lamelo-ball-highlights-ucla-commit-drops-92-points-in-high-school-game/|title=LaMelo Ball highlights: UCLA commit drops 92 points in high school game|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=February 7, 2017|last1=Boone|first1=Kyle|website=''[[CBS_Sports|CBS Sports]]''|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211155519/http://www.cbssports.com/college-basketball/news/lamelo-ball-highlights-ucla-commit-drops-92-points-in-high-school-game/|dead-url=no}}</ref>这在加州高中篮球历史上市表现第二优秀的得分。<ref name="ocregister">{{cite web|url=http://www.ocregister.com/articles/chino-743487-hills-game.html|title=Chino Hills' LaMelo Ball's 92-point game creates a national buzz and a bit of a stir|accessdate=February 9, 2017|date=February 8, 2017|last1=Gardner|first1=Michelle|website=[[Orange_County_Register|Orange County Register]]|archive-date=2017-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170212034951/http://www.ocregister.com/articles/chino-743487-hills-game.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>拉梅洛用比赛来让大家关注对奇诺冈学生亚历克西斯安德森，他被诊断出患有一种罕见的心脏病。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailynews.com/sports/20170208/lamelo-ball-dedicated-his-92-point-game-to-a-classmate-in-need|title=LaMelo Ball dedicated his 92-point game to a classmate in need|accessdate=February 8, 2017|date=February 7, 2017|website=[[Los_Angeles_Daily_News|Los Angeles Daily News]]|archive-date=2017-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170212024946/http://www.dailynews.com/sports/20170208/lamelo-ball-dedicated-his-92-point-game-to-a-classmate-in-need|dead-url=no}}</ref>

